#

Spicy Garlic Butter Shrimp Pasta

25 min
$15
500 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishGluten

Dietary Tags:

SeafoodPastaNut-Free

Cuisine:

ItalianAmerican

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

Quick MealPastaShrimpSpicyGarlic

Description

A quick and flavorful pasta dish with succulent shrimp, garlic, and a spicy kick, all tossed in a buttery sauce.

Ingredients

  • spaghetti: 8 oz
  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • butter: 1/2 cup
  • red pepper flakes: 1 tsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • parsley (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • grated parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
